{"tid":511612,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"(92撚請入) 有感而發, 有冇92巴打覺得童年已經離自己越黎越遠?","createTime":"2017-12-27T16:09:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T02:15:06.000Z","uid":52429,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"ce3f70aa2859b428bbcc3877089f0af00ad7ef4b","tid":511612,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T16:09:09.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小弟尋日Boxing Day去中學同學喺鯉魚門渡假村小教堂嘅婚禮<br />\n個中學同學同未來太太行禮嗰刻我除咗恭喜佢地之外<br />\n忽然間諗到新郎同新娘都係90後<br />\n就諗到轉眼間90後嘅男女已經娶老婆既娶老婆, 嫁人既嫁人<br />\n令我不禁慨嘆90後嘅童年已經離自己越黎越遠<br />\n有冇巴打有同感?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/25659736_1478903582228252_7087534664217425269_n.jpg?oh=7951ee7d3172cf6085386ec7c805d337&amp;oe=5AC5A5D3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F25659736_1478903582228252_7087534664217425269_n.jpg%3Foh%3D7951ee7d3172cf6085386ec7c805d337%26oe%3D5AC5A5D3&h=72ccddec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b036d7185f2fe814da1139efa48a1d6115a660ba","tid":511612,"uid":132296,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T16:12:27.000Z","msg":"二十五歲已經有人結婚生仔<br />\n但我仲係一條毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd8b3b6b47910a1deb59e9fc88477b46bf4e0b50","tid":511612,"uid":52429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b036d7185f2fe814da1139efa48a1d6115a660ba","tid":511612,"uid":132296,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T16:12:27.000Z","msg":"二十五歲已經有人結婚生仔<br />\n但我仲係一條毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T16:18:10.000Z","msg":"係時候要接受自己年紀大咗嘅事實"},{"pid":"b5c747312396428248f2be8a0b15442c908acc87","tid":511612,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T16:25:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c75edbea90dd0d53317de01331538abb7b6ddd6","tid":511612,